==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Therewith
<hw>There*with"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>With
that or this.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧I have learned in whatsoever state I am,
<xex>therewith</xex> to be content.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Phil. iv.
11.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>In addition; besides; moreover.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>To speak of strength and <qex>therewith</qex> hardiness.</q>
<rj><qau>Chaucer.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>At the same time; forthwith.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Johnson.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Therewithal</ent>⟦br⟧
